data.description: Welcome to this charming ranch-style home nestled on nearly 2 acres of picturesque land.  Located in a peaceful and private setting, this property offers the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. It is just minutes off Interstate 85. The inviting front porch welcomes you into this warm and cozy residence. The sprawling lot allows endless possibilities, whether you’re looking to expand your home, create beautiful gardens, or simply enjoy the natural surroundings. The backyard is fenced, providing a secure and private space for outdoor activities. The heart of this home is the generously sized kitchen/dining room combo. It features modern appliances, ample counter space and plenty of storage. New Roof 2022.
